    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cylindrical tapered rods of iron or wood designed to hold a hollow part while it is being forged or turned.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
